So if someone is saying that something you have worked on for years is all in your head while they completely ignore all evidence and results, you just sit quiet, don&#39;t say a word cuz someone might get upset? 

 In the meantime, if some chase only the dark shadows, &quot;investigate&quot; in the dark at night, get growling voices saying &quot;get oput&quot;--that must be the absolute truth!

 There seems to be no way to beat the negativity on this planet. All focus on the darkside, the lies, the misinformation. All seek only fear and evil, the drama, Hollywood fame. No place for truth of anykind or form here. 

 Think I&#39;m done here. 

 F-S


